	<h1 class="title">我们到底需要多少个应用才能跟不同的人说上话啊？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Sam Slaughter</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-17 19:15:02 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19252/medium/19252.jpg?1450325068" alt="" />			
	</div>
